        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502845044" data-ratio="0.5731481481481482" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EC7unEiaL8xoic4shfcURw58h1TBg9RvrM2L7MpwEaAarMOR66dfM6PITAkBAAiaGq3icZretykNSu1r35jvbS2wTg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39);outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);visibility: visible;display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39);outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;">文/六神磊磊</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">一<span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);visibility: visible;display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></strong><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">龙年到了，继续来聊金庸。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">金庸是很喜欢龙的。他的武侠世界，可说是一座巨大的“龙元素宝库”，最好最酷的东西几乎都给了“龙”。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">最刚猛的武功是降龙十八掌，最霸气的神兵利器是屠龙刀，最美的人叫小龙女，另外还有个武林第一美人，是来自海外的黛绮丝，外号紫衫龙王。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">这些龙元素看似很随意，但并不是随笔写来的。可以这么说，在金庸小说里，没有一条龙是随意安排的。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">在他小说里最关键、最重要的几处“龙”的元素，都是和传统文化相关的，甚至直接指代了中华文化的几部经典。今天来给大家揭秘。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><strong style="caret-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">二<span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍‍</span></strong><strong style="caret-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">先从降龙十八掌说起。它代表了哪部经典？当然是《易经》。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">那些威风赫赫的降龙掌招式名：亢龙有悔，飞龙在天，见龙在田，潜龙勿用……都是《易经》的爻辞。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">乔峰对星宿老怪打出一招“亢龙有悔”，等于就是<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">：星宿老怪，我来给你打一卦。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">众所周知，<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">《易经》作为五经之一，是传统文化经典，包含了华夏先民们许多朴素而又深刻的智慧。但除此之外，《易经》还有很丰富的龙图腾元素。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">它的乾卦几乎就是以龙为“主角”的，可以说是一条龙的多姿多彩的一生。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">比如“飞龙在天”，在降龙十八掌里，这是一招从天而降的掌法。它出自乾卦：“九五：飞龙在天，利见大人”。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;">郭靖曾用这一招打得金轮法王差点退了市。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="502845045" data-ratio="0.6781376518218624" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="494" style="height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/EC7unEiaL8xoic4shfcURw58h1TBg9RvrMaVAEIoat7ACthY2x2d7MpTbicSCC0SfpFxFVneM44Ag8nGJHM7TiaaRA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">“飞龙在天”这四个字什么意思呢？就是所谓“以至德而处盛位”，指一个人的德行、修养达到了极高的位置，好比大侠郭靖，义守襄阳，万众景仰，就像一条在天的飞龙。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">又如一招“潜龙勿用”，出自乾卦的“初九：潜龙勿用”。</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">孔子说这一句的意思是：“龙，德而隐者也，不易乎世，不成乎名”，也就是说拥有过人的美德而选择归隐。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">风清扬、令狐冲、袁承志……这些隐于江湖的侠客，都称得上孔子所谓的潜龙。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">降龙十八掌里最著名的一招，就是“亢龙有悔”。所谓“亢龙”，就是越了界、过了头，“知进而不知退，知存而不知亡”，当然要悔之晚矣。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">乾卦里的这一条“龙”，经历过蛰伏，见证了辉煌，也体验了“过犹不及”的道理。这就是祖先用龙的故事所带给我们的启示。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">从这个角度看，降龙十八掌暗合易理，可说是与天地合德，与四时合序，难怪所向无敌。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><strong style="caret-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">三<span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍</span></strong><strong style="caret-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">如果说降龙十八掌代表《易经》，那么</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">金庸小说里第二个著名的“龙”元素——小龙女，同样隐喻了一部名著，就是《庄子》。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">在创作小龙女的形象时，金庸一定是借鉴了《庄子·逍遥游》，不接受反驳：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">“藐姑射之山，有神人居焉，肌肤若冰雪，淖约若处子，不食五谷，吸风饮露，乘云气，御飞龙，而游乎四海之外。”</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">这活脱就是小龙女，容貌绝丽，白衣如雪，居住在与世隔绝的古墓里，睡在寒玉床上，完全就是《庄子》里不食人间烟火的姑射神人。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">另一个旁证是，金庸还给小龙女安排了首词叫《无俗念》，里面有这么一句：</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">“浑似姑射真人，天姿灵秀，意气殊高洁。”</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">再次提到姑射真人。小龙女的形象源于《庄子》，应该没有争议了吧。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">说回到龙，”降龙十八掌“是借用了龙的威猛刚健，小龙女这个形象则是用了龙的神秘、高洁。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">她是金庸小说里来历最神秘的女主角，无父无母，无名无姓，也没有乡里籍贯。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">被终南山古墓收养后，得名“龙女“，也是隐喻了她的传奇色彩，就像从云天之外降临到尘世一样。<br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">小龙女不但形象、气质符合《庄子》，她为人也很淡然、淳朴、天真，深得道家豁达无为的气质。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">人人都为“武林盟主”争破头，偏偏她不争不抢：“我做不来什么盟主不盟主”，半点也不放在心上。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="502845046" data-ratio="0.7425925925925926" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/EC7unEiaL8xoic4shfcURw58h1TBg9RvrMpkAvdxDkPUFWfhP6uUy1pOfLOqAohvbI3dkheiaeczl3Vvu3zBEf1Sw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">面对金轮法王挑衅：“你若接不住我十招，那该怎样？”，她一句“接不住就接不住，又怎样了？”让法王语塞。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">同样是一个“龙”的元素，在<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">降龙十八掌和《易经》中，就让人感到睿智、健旺、向上，而放在小龙女和《庄子》身上，就让人觉得飘逸、洒脱。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">正像中国文化的丰富多彩，既<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">看得懂、算得明，也想得开、放得下；可以自强不息、勇猛精进，也可以逍遥游于天地之间。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><strong style="caret-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">四<span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍</span></strong><strong style="caret-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">再下一样金庸小说里重要的龙元素，毫无争议，是屠龙宝刀。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">它所指代的是中华传统文化里另一类瑰宝——兵法。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">宝刀百炼生玄光，秘笈兵书此中藏。屠龙刀有个最大秘密，就是其中藏有兵法武穆遗书。</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">郭靖黄蓉当初铸造这把刀，是希望未来有志之士能取出兵书，驱逐鞑虏，恢复中华，所以刀名“屠龙”。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">夭矫如龙的宝刀，在金庸笔下，也成了传统文化里兵战智慧、勇武精神的指代。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">事实上，龙在传统文化里有一个含义，就是战争之神。所谓<span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">龙战于野，其血玄黄。当初</span>黄帝大战蚩尤，就曾召唤<span style="letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">应龙相助，攻蚩尤于<span style="letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">冀州之野。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍‍‍</span></span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍‍</span></span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">金庸为什么要在武侠小说里嵌入“兵法”这么一条“龙”？大概是因为</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">兵法也代表一种民族精神，就是战斗精神和反抗精神。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">中华民族一直是爱好和平的，反对穷兵黩武。<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">《六韬》就有云：“兵为凶器，不得已而用之。”</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;">但我们也同样能征善战、名将辈出，所以我们的军事思想也光辉灿烂。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">仅一部《孙子兵法》迄今就已有2500多年的历史了，直到今天，“上兵伐谋”、“知己知彼，百战不殆”、“攻其无备，出其不意”、“投之亡地然后存，陷之死地然后生”等名言仍然脍炙人口。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;">屠龙刀，是金庸小说中凌厉的一道寒光，也是千百年来华夏民族不屈、反抗的历史的写照。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="502845047" data-ratio="0.755" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="400" style="height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/EC7unEiaL8xoic4shfcURw58h1TBg9RvrMppwIjdkVVkMKXuKvW8TnwVlkd5Ex6pS3x9HbicDhDdZgDn74TuaBxDQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><strong style="caret-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">五<span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></strong><strong style="caret-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">金庸小说还有一处“龙”的重要设定——“天龙八部”，它代表的是又一种文化经典，佛经和佛学。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">佛学是外来的，千百年里和中华传统文化相融合，开枝散叶，早已经融汇成了传统文化中的一部分。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">“天龙八部”本身就出自佛经。它的原意是指八种神道生灵，“龙”也是生灵中的一种，而在金庸笔下，它隐喻的是林林总总的众生。<span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">写《天龙八部》的时候，金庸已经对佛学有了浓厚兴趣。整部小说也笼罩着一股悲悯的气氛，所谓“无人不冤，有情皆孽”。<span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">慕容复、鸠摩智、段正淳、叶二娘、康敏……小说里这一个个好汉恶汉、怨女痴男，都是被隐喻的“天龙八部”，他们都是欲望的奴隶，被名利、执念等束缚、折磨，</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">某种程度上，他们都是被悲悯的对象。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">读金庸小说，常会觉得苍凉厚重，又不失温暖，就是因为有这一份悲悯在。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="502845051" data-ratio="0.6259259259259259" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/EC7unEiaL8xoic4shfcURw58h1TBg9RvrMajyQCImcbjz7Ol9kEwsnFEzxf9VSJmp9uK1K7BZCeLC3Mgn7c2V9Eg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">回头看金庸小说里这些著名的“龙”元素，不难发现，<span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">“龙”一直是最抢镜、最亮眼的文化名片，但它的含义又非常丰富多彩，始终在嬗变之中。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">假如把它们合起来，金庸笔下的“龙”，恰好是一个华夏<span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">文明延续的故事：<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍‍‍‍</span></span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">《易经》诞生的时代，古老的先祖仰观星象，思索生命宇宙的规律。</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">春秋时，兵家争雄，涌现出了《孙子兵法》一类的杰作，为人们争夺生存空间。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">在无尽的征伐中，出现了庄子这样的智者，开始去看透、解脱，追求一种终极的自在。而且</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">我们还渐渐有了更多的悲悯、同情的精神，融汇入儒释道等不同的文化之中，一直延续到今天。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size: 17px;"><strong>六</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">金庸小说对龙的诠释，也给人一种启示：<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">图腾，是要继承和发展的，它的含义也不会永远一成不变。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">文学、电影、绘画……每一次新的创造，其实都是在延续传统，但同时也给龙不一样的意义。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">我小时候有部特别火的儿童剧《小龙人》，<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">里面的小龙人会吃饼干、唱儿歌、喝酸奶。这就是非常有颠覆性的，很多人都是第一次看到那么童真可爱的龙。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">无独有偶，后来在动画片《哪吒》里，原著中的恶龙敖丙也变成了哪吒的朋友，很受人喜欢。<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">这等于就是给民族图腾赋予了理解、友谊、认同的新意义。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">像金庸先生一样，让图腾“活”起来，甚至变成我们亲切的朋友，才是致敬传统的最好的方式。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">而最近，我看到最有趣的一次对“龙”的致敬和再创造，就是王者龙耀了，发音没错，我是重庆的。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">龙年门槛上，他们家推出了非常酷炫的龙年系列限定皮肤。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">王者荣耀对传统文化是有很深情结的，这已经是他们第很多次致敬传统了。之前的</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">长城守卫军就特别成功，导致我迷了很长一段时间的守约。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这次荣耀龙年限定皮肤的主题也很大气，叫“龙祐千载”，</span>分别有星象、青铜、兵戈、诗歌、海贸等几个主题，等于是说龙的精神从方方面面支撑着我们，延续着华夏的文化。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">怀疑主创是不是偷看过金庸，里面的寓意简直和金庸小说里的“龙”一脉相承。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;">“星象”主题龙皮是孙尚香的，它让人很难不想起《易经》，祖先们仰观天文，细察万物，以龙的名义书写成华美的<span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">爻辞，破解天地的隐秘。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="text-align: center;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">“兵戈”主题的孙策龙皮，自然而然会让人想到万兵之王屠龙刀。龙在这里也代表着战斗、不屈、勇武，伴随着华夏一族征战沙场，守护家园。<br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">另外，这款龙皮的设计也是我最喜欢的，它的</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">色系是龙战于野的烟霞赤，非常耐看。</span><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;">总之，<span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">“龙</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">”</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span>对中国人来说是个特殊的符号，它是传承，是团聚，是守护，“龙<span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">祐千载</span>”，它<span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;">是我们民族生生不息的象征。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;">如这次赵子龙的台词：<span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);">奏黄钟，歌大吕，上祀九霄澄明，下祈四海永清。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="502845057" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/EC7unEiaL8xpTW3mia0viaDsN2iawVU4O5Je6Njhqg2m7NPkCq1Fe5xzuFJzD8k3qN7icoTp7OLUTtLJLKEKcJfzVicw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;">龙年我们一聚成龙，祝所有的华夏儿女龙年大吉。</span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p>]]></summary>
